    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently overhauled for peak volumetric efficiency. This example utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, providing tactile engagement and direct power delivery to the rear wheels via a limited-slip differential. The chassis has undergone essential subframe reinforcement, a critical upgrade for structural rigidity during high-lateral G-load cornering. Suspension components feature refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the original M-tuned kinematics. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust, exhibiting a linear power curve and the signature metallic exhaust note synonymous with Bavarian engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
